body_html:
@DenisN03 , one class + background.
It took around 1.6 seconds with quantization on a Huawei P10 Lite with 200x200 images. With smaller images, quality was very bad.
We are currently trying MobileUNet. First results show 0.86 seconds without quantization and 224x224 images.
We would also like to try Mask RCNN at some point.

body:
@DenisN03 , one class + background.
It took around 1.6 seconds with quantization on a Huawei P10 Lite with 200x200 images. With smaller images, quality was very bad.
We are currently trying [MobileUNet](https://github.com/akirasosa/mobile-semantic-segmentation). First results show 0.86 seconds without quantization and 224x224 images.
We would also like to try Mask RCNN at some point.
